From the Planet Crypton, StarBoy got thrown out of orbit and is lost in the cosmos.
He needs our guidance. We need to band together, to save our poor wandering soul – and guide him to a new home, among the stars.
Help StarBoy take off by hodling $STARBOY tokens!

Our goal is simple. Get StarBoy back to space, fairly.

To accomplish this we will be running an extremely small presale. We have noticed time and time again that devs get greedy and try to aim for large presales to profit personally, this only hurts the potential and causes a huge dumping ground for presellers.

Our presale will consist of a 20/20 bnb split, we are raising a minimal amount for the LP.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][vc_column_text]

How it works:

20 bnb is whitelisted through Unicrypt and will be awarded to random community members who complete shill tasks with proof. This is a way for us to reward you for helping us grow.

10 bnb will be public to keep it fair.

Min: 0.1
Max: 0.5

We are using Unicrypt to help combat Dxsale’s bot issues.
